    What is image of a product?
    Product images are photographs of the product you are selling. Businesses use product images for marketing their products through ads, posters, and eCommerce shops or websites. An excellent product image should attract potential customers and leave a lasting impression on the product.

    What makes a good product image?
    Give as many different viewpoints as possible to highlight key features of your product. An all-around view is more engaging and can help shoppers envision themselves wearing or using your product, which can lead to more sales in your store. It's also important to include close-up shots of your products as well.16-Aug-2023
